      </p>
      <div class="flex justify-center space-x-4">
        <a href="/login" class="bg-transparent border border-white text-white py-2 px-4 rounded hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition">
          Log In
        </a>
        <a href="/register" class="bg-transparent border border-white text-white py-2 px-4 rounded hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition">
